name: HIC (Alphabet Spectrum)
description: The word HIC is turned into light and colours, making the spectral energy of the word visible. By proportionally mapping the alphabet to the visible light spectrum, each letter in the alphabet is paired with a colour, and words are visualized with sequences of colours. — Coded in Processing. 2020, Zoltan Szalay — https://www.instagram.com/insgraphizm/
